<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">

<xsl:param name="subjectId"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ServiceOrder"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ServiceOrder"> <BusinessPartnerCommunication_PartnerSelection Id="{@Id}" refBusinessPartnerCommunicationSubjectId="{$subjectId}" IsNewPartner="false" refBusinessPartnerId="{@refBusinessPartnerId}" refCurrencyId="{AS:GetConstant('LocalCurrencyId')}" ShowPartnerSelection="false" > </BusinessPartnerCommunication_PartnerSelection>
<ShoppingCart Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" DateIssued="{date:date()}" refCurrencyId="{AS:GetConstant('LocalCurrencyId')}" >
<xsl:apply-templates select="ServiceOrderItem"/> </ShoppingCart> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ServiceOrderItem"> <ShoppingCartItem Id="{@Id}" PriceEntry="{@PriceLocal}" Quantity="{@Quantity}" refProductId="{@refProductId}" DiscountPct1="{@DiscountPct1}" DiscountPct2="{@DiscountPct2}" > </ShoppingCartItem> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: ServiceOrderItem_LoadServices
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:param name="itemId"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ServiceDefinition"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ServiceDefinition"> <Service Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refServiceOrderItemId="{$itemId}" refServiceDefinitionId="{@Id}" refServiceStateId="{AS:LookupValue('ceabf9a1-931d-4c77-879b-98940726e2af', @refServiceTypeId)}" refServiceTypeId="{@refServiceTypeId}" > <xsl:apply-templates select="ServiceDefinitionParameter"/> </Service> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ServiceDefinitionParameter"> <ServiceParameter Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refServiceDefinitionParameterId="{@Id}" refServiceDefintionParameterOptionId="{@refInitialServiceDefintionParameterOptionId}" TextValue="{@InitialTextValue}" /> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: Service_OnCreated
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="Service"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="Service"> <xsl:variable name="serviceDefinitionCode" select="AS:LookupValue('09a42c3e-e934-4b21-afe5-655ff90e2bcc', @refServiceDefinitionId)"/>
<xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="ReferenceCode"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:GenerateSerial($serviceDefinitionCode)"/> </xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: ServiceOrder_OnCreated
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ServiceOrder"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ServiceOrder"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="ReferenceCode"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:GenerateSerial('ServiceOrder', @DateOrdered)"/> </xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: ServiceOrder_SetValidated
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <!-- only orders which have not been validated before --> <xsl:apply-templates select="ServiceOrder[not(string(@DateValidated))]"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ServiceOrder"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="refServiceOrderStateId"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:GetConstant('ServiceOrderState_Validated')"/> </xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="DateValidated"> <xsl:value-of select="date:date-time()"/> </xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
